# Segment Tree Beats

[Video](https://youtu.be/NwkO73jGSPA?si=7biJi9WYqQchKO7Y)

Basic idea is if we take modulo, square root operation in a range, then the array element decrease by at least half.
And with strong break condition e.g. max > 1 in case of square root range update or max > modulo in case of range modulo
we can achieve O(nlogn * log(a_max)) time complexity where a_max = max(arr).

Implemented Examples
1. Range Update: %=  
   Point Update: :=  
   Range Query: +  
   [Question](https://codeforces.com/group/1rv4rhCsHp/contest/327313/problem/A)
2. Range Update: square root
   Range Query: +
   [Question](https://www.spoj.com/problems/GSS4/)
